metadata.abstract: 1. The action of the Etobicoke York Community Council on the 10th day of January, 2012, taken under the delegated authority of Sections 27-149B and 27-152 of Chapter 27, Council Procedures, of The City of Toronto Municipal Code, in respect of Items 12.12, 12.13, 12.14, 12.15, 12.16, 12.17, 12.18, 12.19, 12.20, 12.21, 12.22, 12.23, 12.24, 12.25, 12.26, 12.27, 12.28, 12.29, 12.30, 12.31, 12.32, 12.33, 12.35, 12.36, 12.37, 12.38, 12.39, 12.40, 12.44, 12.47 and 12.48 of the Etobicoke York Community Council, up to and including the enactment of this Confirmatory By-law at 1:18 p.m. this day, and in respect of each motion, resolution and other action, passed and taken under delegated authority including the enactment of any previous Confirmatory By-laws in respect of the meeting, is adopted, ratified and confirmed.
